title: BONUS: Movie Mike's Movie Podcast - Most Famous Movie Set In Each State - Northeast (Part 1) Movie Review: Project Power (Netflix)
itunes:title: BONUS: Movie Mike's Movie Podcast - Most Famous Movie Set In Each State - Northeast (Part 1) Movie Review: Project Power (Netflix)
description:
This is Part 1 of a 4-Part Series where Movie Mike tries to answer the question: What's the most famous movie that takes place in each state of the US? This episode covers the Northeast. Mike also reviews the new Netflix movie “Project Power” starringJamie Foxx, Joseph Gordon-Levitt, Dominique Fishback and Machine Gun Kelly. Plus a review of ‘Sky High’ with his girlfriend’s 14 year old brother Houston to celebrate the movies 15 year anniversary. 


To nominate your movie from your state click HERE or follow mike on Twitter @mikedeestro.


New Episodes Every Monday!
